text: "The Mosquito" is a 1972 song by The Doors and was taken from their eighth studio album Full Circle. It went to number 17 in the Netherlands, number 15 in Finland and Austria and number 25 in Germany. It was covered by French singer Joe Dassin. == References == Category:1972 songs Category:The Doors songs Category:Joe Dassin songs
